>>2343d3f8-4dbe-4d58-a60a-37ef87faf4f8
>Nigger, tor started blocking http traffic.
Tor just blindly relays TCP traffic unless it has been instructed to otherwise. If you were unable to send HTTP through Tor you might've just gotten unlucky with the exit node. But I doubt they would block HTTP, the problem was probably somewhere else.
